CHANGELOG

0.2   May 2017

Browser-based UI

* Clipy is now an aiohttp web-app
* Vid.me support added

0.1   September 2014

Curses-based UI

* Focussing on command-line
* Use asyncio instead of threads
* Pafy YouTube API module no longer used in UI
* Python 3 only now, asyncronous via Python asyncio library, app & ui integrated
* Modules spit out from ui
* Local server
* Logging
* YouTube only
